{"tid":1367673,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"做得義士預左比人拉 預左要坐啦","createTime":"2019-07-26T10:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:14:38.000Z","uid":126115,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2708f85c79459ba124683abe5c79a7b3aea5e2a3","tid":1367673,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"今時今日既局面 做得勇武派衝得最前就預左比黑警拉<br />\n見到有圍中聯辦既義士比人拉 唔該你地唔好好出奇咁<br />\n掟隻蛋都比人拉咁離譜？ 係咁離譜架啦<br />\n唔好諗住籌旗幫佢地打官司會有用 <br />\n唔好諗住搵到證據就可以還佢地清白<br />\n冇撚用架 欲加之罪 何患無辭<br />\n天琦佢地依家咪又係坐緊 七警咪又係上訴到 689咪又係唔洗告<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界係好撚簡單 成王敗寇<br />\n好似孫中山咁革命成功前只係逃犯 通緝犯<br />\n只有革命成功之後 佢先係國父<br />\n<br />\n如果我地今次運動衰左 呢班比人拉既係歷史上只係罪犯 而唔係義士<br />\n只有運動成功 林鄭同佢班狗官一齊收皮 先可以幫呢班義士正名<br />\n<br />\n如果要幫呢班義士 只有一個方法 就係令當權者跪低<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#五大訴求 一個都不能少</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"976be36c924e50af122be0c6800a5caa7eb77f3e","tid":1367673,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1a1a9331239f6e2fe1b42801a6955814406516","tid":1367673,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafa5aee65c3319544a8b58444bf64c739d203e8","tid":1367673,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:35:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#五大訴求 一個都不能少</span>"},{"pid":"720c9a3b7a6b33d15b8fccb4bf22063f97d9ad8a","tid":1367673,"uid":269459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:36:35.000Z","msg":"歷史就係咁"},{"pid":"27a4976f052dc9722da3380f8aed89a79a329c91","tid":1367673,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e